### Role API recipes

# Check allow (eventual)
POST http://localhost:8088/v2/check?consistency=eventual
Content-Type: application/json
X-Role-Consistency: eventual

{
  "tenant": "t1",
  "subject": "user:1",
  "relation": "viewer",
  "resource": "doc:42",
  "context": {
    "ip": "127.0.0.1"
  }
}

### Explain
POST http://localhost:8088/v2/check/explain
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenant": "t1",
  "subject": "user:1",
  "relation": "viewer",
  "resource": "doc:42"
}

### JWKS
GET http://localhost:8088/v2/admin/keys/jwks
